the flowers readily available in stores.

20:33.315 --> 20:36.199
I'm a hero, the flowers are saved...

20:36.304 --> 20:38.702
Laroche and nature win.

20:39.953 --> 20:41.517
Great.

20:41.726 --> 20:43.916
Did you get that last part?

20:44.020 --> 20:45.897
Yeah, I sure did.

20:46.001 --> 20:49.094
Orchids are the sexiest flowers
on Earth.

