intellectual...

34:30.070 --> 34:33.197
with whom you do the Sunday
Times crossword puzzle in bed.

34:33.302 --> 34:36.014
One looks like a Midwestern
beauty queen.

34:36.118 --> 34:38.411
One looks like Amelia.

34:38.516 --> 34:40.289
One has eyes that dance.

