Really? Come on.

38:35.528 --> 38:38.344
Hey, it's Amelia.

38:38.969 --> 38:40.325
Hey, Amelia!

38:40.638 --> 38:44.079
Hey, Donald. Hey, Charlie.

38:44.600 --> 38:48.927
- Hey. Hi there.
